# Environment Variables for InboxPrism Deployment

## Backend Environment Variables (Render)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
GMAIL_CLIENT_ID=your_gmail_oauth_client_id
GMAIL_CLIENT_SECRET=your_gmail_oauth_client_secret
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./emails.db
CORS_ORIGINS=https://your-frontend-domain.vercel.app

## Frontend Environment Variables (Vercel)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.onrender.com

## Notes:
# 1. Replace all placeholder values with your actual credentials
# 2. For Gmail OAuth, create credentials at: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 3. For OpenAI API key, get it from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# 4. Update CORS_ORIGINS with your actual Vercel frontend URL
# 5. Update NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL with your actual Render backend URL
